<br>
My Goals.<br>
Not be KOS in Freeport<br>
Be able to Train in Freeport<br>
Sell and buy in Freeport<br>
Bank in Freeport<br>
<br>
<br>
My questions.<br>
<br>
1. Can someone point me a to a nice page with this documented with a simple step by step, so we don't have to re-event the wheel here. <br>
<br>
2. How many different KOS factions do I need to worry about?  I read some posts and didn't realize there are guards in North Freeport that are different from the ones at the gate.<br>
<br>
3. Who do you turn the Deathfist belts into?  I was turning my belts into a guy &quot;I forgot his Name&quot; in the warrior guild on the second floor by the arena, or Number 6 on WFP map from EQAtlas.  He was giving me experience, some faction and gold, but is it the faction that I need.<br>
<br>
4.  Never been to Nektulos Forest before, but in one post someone mention that there is a camp with around 13 Orcs in it. Do these orcs drop belts?  Are these the same Orcs as in EC for faction hits? <br>
<br>
5. Will this same method work for a Troll Shadow Knight and an Iksar Necromancer.<br>
<br>
6. How many must DIE!!!!!  I have kill what seems like to me a lot with my Iksar Necro and my friends Troll SK grouped. We got 2 levels by  just killing them and only them.  Still we canâ€™t get into town.<br>
<br>
7.  Add anything thing that you think I missed from this list and would help me.<br>
<br>
<br>
