<br>
While you are killing orcs loot all the deathfist belts that drop and when you are full run them to EFP and give to the captain in the militia house...it may take 100-150 belts to get dubious to them, once you hit dubious you are good to go.<br>
<br>
Now keep killin those orcs so you can get amiable to the monk guild, once you have done so you can do the white sash quest over and over and everything gets really easy from there, once you hit ally (which comes quickly) at monks you'll be good to go in NFP. <br>
<br>
HINT: when doing the white sash quest run around ec and wc and buy all the deathfist pawn scalps, bone chips and snake fangs you can, makes the faction raising much quicker.<br>
<br>
